code: import axios from'axios';import{version}from'react';const url='http://localhost:8000/tipovehiculo/api/v1/tipovehiculo/';export const obtenerTipoV=async()=>{const response=await axios.get(url);return response.data;};export const crearTipoV=async vehiculo=>{const response=await axios.post(url,vehiculo);return response.data;};export const eliminarTipoV=async id=>{const response=await axios.delete("http://localhost:8000/tipovehiculo/api/v1/tipovehiculo/".concat(id,"/"));return response.data;};export const actualizarTipoV=async(id,vehiculo)=>{const response=await axios.put("http://localhost:8000/tipovehiculo/api/v1/tipovehiculo/".concat(id,"/"),vehiculo);return response.data;};
